dc_title_s: Atlantis insula à Nicolao Sanson antiquitati restituta; nunc demum majori forma delineata, et in decem regna, iuxta decem Neptuni filios distributa: Praeterea insualae, nostraeqr. contenentis regiones quibus imperavere Atlantici reges; aut quas armis tentavere ex conatibus geographicus; Gulielmi Sanson Nicolai filii.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. State 1. 1 map: hand col.; 40 x 57 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
